- For Directory listing: Site: rohan-website.com AND intitle: “index of”
- For finding backup files: site: rohan-website.com AND (ext: “backup” OR ext: “bak” OR ext: ”old”)
- Finding internal server errors: site: rohan-website.com AND (intitle: 500) 
- Finding sensitive parameters in URL: site: rohan-website.com AND (inurl: “api” OR inurl: “apikey” OR inurl: “session” OR inurl: “apitoken”) 
- Finding HTTP pages: site: rohan-website.com AND (-inurl: https) 
- For SQL error (debug) pages:
  - Site: rohan-website.com AND (“mysql error with query” OR “mysqli_connect” OR ” mysqli_query” OR “pdo_mysql”)
  - Site: rohan-website.com AND (“[MICROSOFT][ODBC SQ”] OR “[SQL SERVER]”)
- Use robots.txt file to restrict search engines to index sensitive files.
- External Resources:
  - https://www.exploit-db.com/google-hacking-database
  - Google Hacking for Pentesters by Jhonny Long: https://www.blackhat.com/presentations/bh-europe-05/BH_EU_05-Long.pdf

